title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Zinc & Related Articles
description: Imports of Intra EU - Zinc & Related Articles in the United Kingdom increased to 17.24 GBP Million in September from 3.17 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Zinc & Related Articles in the United Kingdom averaged 6.14 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 26.15 GBP Million in November of 2006 and a record low of 1.06 GBP Million in February of 2003. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Zinc & Related Articles.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
